    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam官方交流1群：1067449843</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该作为demo内容，由于全作流程短，demo将会展现游戏的背景以及人物的基本介绍，demo流程将有0.5小时左右的游玩时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感兴趣请试玩，谢谢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/8a722b7d6477bf0d68e7c70288f4aadb.avif?t=1766134390\" width=614 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在充满神秘与未知的90年代架空世界里，一家鲜为人知的私人实验室机构在城市内一处隐秘的角落悄然运作着！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/19a6807464bac98bf445cadd119fa04d.poster.avif?t=1766134390\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/19a6807464bac98bf445cadd119fa04d.webm?t=1766134390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/19a6807464bac98bf445cadd119fa04d.mp4?t=1766134390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“他”胆颤心惊，一路奔逃。慌不择路间，“他”躲进了一间位于城市郊区略显沧桑陈旧的别墅。一眼望去，别墅被周围高大的树木层层遮挡，枝叶在风中沙沙作响，林间的鸟鸣声仿佛诉说着无数的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏时，你将作为主人公”安戴德“，因”特殊“的工作需要被安排住进这间别墅，并在无意中与阁楼的“他”日夜相伴，一起度过接下来有趣的日子！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/35545ad8f06db643fafa5acd0395bae3.poster.avif?t=1766134390\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/35545ad8f06db643fafa5acd0395bae3.webm?t=1766134390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/35545ad8f06db643fafa5acd0395bae3.mp4?t=1766134390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/4c9cb7cd712f3471636ecff40abccd7d.avif?t=1766134390\" width=614 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以喂养“他”不同的食物，教习日常的生活行为，记录不断变化的生长数据等等，沉浸式感受养成乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为没有感情的赚钱机器？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为关系亲密的生活伴侣？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为并肩作战的靠谱战友？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >.......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一切皆有可能！！！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/360c1fde2480d0e12ed4002ce5a025a1.poster.avif?t=1766134390\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/360c1fde2480d0e12ed4002ce5a025a1.webm?t=1766134390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/360c1fde2480d0e12ed4002ce5a025a1.mp4?t=1766134390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/f400c40300923d5f96beefbbc05b119a.avif?t=1766134390\" width=614 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏当前设定14个不同结局，完全不同的分支剧情以及每个阶段不同的养成小剧场将带你感受一次次交换人生！每一次不同的选择亦将改变大家的命运！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/77b7cdbe41ea5bcd4e38b1a37b073058.poster.avif?t=1766134390\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/77b7cdbe41ea5bcd4e38b1a37b073058.webm?t=1766134390\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3318020/extras/77b7cdbe41ea5bcd4e38b1a37b073058.mp4?t=1766134390\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幸福生活还是魔鬼深渊，一切皆在你的一念之间！</p>",
